org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.resourcemanager

类 RMActiveServiceContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.resourcemanager.RMActiveServiceContext

  • @InterfaceAudience.Private
@InterfaceStability.Unstable
public class RMActiveServiceContext
extends Object
    The RMActiveServiceContext is the class that maintains all the RMActiveService contexts.This is expected to be used only by ResourceManager and RMContext.
